\texttt{expl3} package and in case you are curious how I did the font replacement see the expl3 manual 0.5.7 section 6.5.3 (Paragraphs and Lines) 

\ExplSyntaxOn
\cs_new_nopar_new:Npn \setreplacedfont #1 { %
    \fontexchange{#1} %
    \ exchangedit {Proportional} {Normal\ Ref\ Math} %
} 
\cs_new_nopar_new:Npn \fontexchange #1 #2 { %
    \grp_open:nn {#1} #2 { N \mathit{ng } \strut} %
    \grp_open:nn {#2} { W \mathit{r} \mathit{d } \strut} %
    \map_open:nn {W \mathit{r} \mathit{d} }{ D \mathit{t} \mathit{o } \strut} %
    \grp_open:nn {#2} { Y \mathit{m} \mathit{a} \strut} %
    \grp_open:nn {#1} { E \mathit{g} \mathit{a} \strut} %
} 
\ExplSyntaxOff 
